; -

DRWSTAT      ; TODO:
                ; 1. HMMV: fill row 25 with COL_UI (clear bar)
                ; 2. Render LANG text (LGNONE/Z80/BASIC/C/PYTHON → string)
                ; 3. Render INS/OVR
                ; 4. Render Ln:DOCLINE+1/TOTLINES
                ; 5. Render Col:CURX+1
                ; 6. Render FILENAME (truncated to fit)
                RET


